{"tid":2197473,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"年輕人感染率急增 熱衷聚會容易播疫","createTime":"2020-09-10T15:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T16:03:02.000Z","uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"926a4f718297bd6f38c457ea671b1e3849181d0a","tid":2197473,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:33:55.000Z","msg":"英國因應新冠肺炎疫情反彈，英格蘭由下周一（14日）起實施6人限聚令。有英國傳染病學家表示，不少年輕人於疫情期間仍然聚會，年輕人新冠肺炎感染率明顯上升，更憂慮年輕人會將病毒傳播給家中長者。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1Q6bst.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1Q6bst.png&h=28b69fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴斯大學傳染病微生物學家普雷斯頓（Andrew Preston）也表示，隨著國家重新開放，預計學生感染病例將會大增。他呼籲政府增加檢測範圍，以找出社區中的無症狀患者，避免他們將病毒傳播給其他人。"},{"pid":"cd2199992ecae2415053f45d2d222fdc7624d998","tid":2197473,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e61da41e0647459a700f46e9c54865470d3537","tid":2197473,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T16:03:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">武漢肺炎</span></span></strong>"}]}